DFIReballz — Investigation Output Directory
============================================

This directory is bind-mounted into the Claude Code container at /workspace/output.
All investigation findings produced by the AI are saved here so you can access
them directly on your host machine.

Directory Structure
-------------------

  findings/     Analysis results, summaries, IOC lists, MITRE ATT&CK mappings.
                The AI writes structured output here after completing analyses.

  screenshots/  Captured screenshots and visual evidence.
                Any screen captures or diagrams produced during investigation.

  logs/         Investigation activity logs and audit trails.
                Session logs, tool invocation records, chain of custody entries.

  exports/      Exported artifacts: carved files, extracted objects, PCAPs.
                Files extracted from evidence by forensic tools (foremost,
                tshark --export-objects, bulk_extractor, etc.).

  timelines/    Reconstructed event timelines.
                Chronological event reconstructions from filesystem, network,
                and memory analysis.

Notes
-----
- Evidence files go in ../evidence/ (mounted read-only in containers).
- Reports go in ../reports/ (forensic reports in HTML/PDF/Markdown).
- This directory is for working output only — not evidence or final reports.
